reviewText: Boring nothing like the first one which was very inspiring.

I can't speak for the content personally but my daughter loves it! She's a huge One Direction fan so of course it doesn't take much to impress her. Anything One Direction is good by her. So far, I have no complaints though!
I enjoyed my DVD Recommend it for all True Directioners out their!
The disc was not great it was shaky for the first few minutes the quality was bad and it was not what I was expecting.
I thought it was going to be more than music and do your stuff. Not interviews
i knew it was a rip off, u could see all these online, but i just like keeping CD of it :D so i wouldnt reccommend buying it unless u just want a cop of 3 interviews
